  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 7071.56 sitting below the GEX flip at 7107, dealers are in PIN regime and likely buying this dip given the strong positive gamma wall at 7100 (+4551.4M) providing immediate support. The massive gamma concentration between 7100-7200 creates a powerful magnet effect, with dealers expected to sell any rally toward the 7200 max gamma strike (+6781.5M) and continue buying weakness back toward 7100. Key levels to monitor are the 7107 flip line for regime changes and the 7040 negative gamma pocket where accelerated buying would kick in if breached.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pulled back toward the 7100-7150 range with limited downside.",
